title: Elderberries Cafe
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, American, Raw, Juice bar, Take-out
description: Books and drinks cafe offering a menu of smoothies and juices, light vegan food and raw food. Has salads, sandwiches and wraps with Daiya cheese, raw soups, smoothies with house-made almond mylk or cashew mylk. Vegan except for honey option in drinks. Atmosphere is very casual. Parking on street or in back.
